exhibitor (1.7.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Added command line option to specify address for HTTP server to listen on
  * Restore all backups upon starting
  * Fixed a bug in servo where Zookeeper metrics were not reset to 0
  * Support relative path to ZooKeeper

 -- Tancredi Orlando <tancredi.orlando@gmail.com>  Fri, 16 Feb 2018 13:30:00 +0100

exhibitor (1.6.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * First release since migration out from Netflix to Soabase, new group ID io.soabase.exhibitor
  * Add support for Consul shared configuration
  * Ported to maven
  * AWS SDK version to 1.11.128 (from 1.10.24)

 -- Tancredi Orlando <tancredi.orlando@gmail.com>  Sun, 14 Jan 2018 22:00:00 +0100
